<plot>The troubled production of _Winter Kills (1979)_(qv) is covered here in this documentary with interviews with a few cast and crew members. The film was shut down 3 times, and to save the production they had to make _American Success Company (1980)_(qv) to get themselves out of debt. They also talk about the first time director and the "old crew" that was used.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?655089</url></doc>
